list.name: runs
list.query: select title, text, tags from events where $timeFilter AND "tags" =~ /$group/ AND "tags"  =~ /$page/ AND "tags" =~ /$browser/ AND "tags" =~  /$connectivity/ AND "tags" =~  /$category/

panels.description: The first visual change is when something for the first time is painted within the current viewport. It is calculated by analyzing a video recording of the screen.

targets.query: SELECT last("median") FROM "autogen"."FirstVisualChange" WHERE "group" =~ /^$group$/ AND "browser" =~ /^$browser$/ AND "connectivity" =~ /^$connectivity$/ AND "page" =~ /^$page$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)

panels.title: First Visual Change

panels.description: The Speed Index is the average time at which visible parts of the page are displayed. It is expressed in milliseconds and dependent on size of the view port. It was created by Pat Meenan and you can checkout the full documentation [here](https://sites.google.com/a/webpagetest.org/docs/using-webpagetest/metrics/speed-index).

targets.query: SELECT last("median") FROM "autogen"."SpeedIndex" WHERE "group" =~ /^$group$/ AND "browser" =~ /^$browser$/ AND "connectivity" =~ /^$connectivity$/ AND "page" =~ /^$page$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)

panels.title: Speed Index

panels.description: The visual complete 85% is when 85% (or more) are finished within the current viewport. It is calculated by analyzing a video recording of the screen.

targets.query: SELECT last("median") FROM "autogen"."VisualComplete85" WHERE "group" =~ /^$group$/ AND "browser" =~ /^$browser$/ AND "connectivity" =~ /^$connectivity$/ AND "page" =~ /^$page$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)

panels.title: Visual Complete 85%

panels.description: The last visual change is when something for the last time is changing within the current viewport. It is calculated by analyzing a video recording of the screen.

targets.query: SELECT last("median") FROM "autogen"."LastVisualChange" WHERE "group" =~ /^$group$/ AND "browser" =~ /^$browser$/ AND "connectivity" =~ /^$connectivity$/ AND "page" =~ /^$page$/ AND "summaryType" = 'pageSummary' AND "category" =~ /^$category$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)

panels.title: Last Visual Change

panels.description: Fully loaded time when the last of all assets is downloaded on the page. It is calculated using the Resource Timing API where we use the last downloaded asset.

targets.query: SELECT last("median") FROM "autogen"."fullyLoaded" WHERE "group" =~ /^$group$/ AND "browser" =~ /^$browser$/ AND "connectivity" =~ /^$connectivity$/ AND "page" =~ /^$page$/ AND "summaryType" = 'pageSummary' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)

panels.title: Fully Loaded

targets.query: SELECT last("value") FROM "autogen"."requests" WHERE "group" =~ /^$group$/ AND "browser" =~ /^$browser$/ AND "connectivity" =~ /^$connectivity$/ AND "page" =~ /^$page$/ AND "summaryType" = 'pageSummary' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)

panels.description: The total transfer size over the wire (compressed size if your asset is compressed) of all assets on the page.

targets.query: SELECT last("value") FROM "autogen"."transferSize" WHERE "group" =~ /^$group$/ AND "browser" =~ /^$browser$/ AND "connectivity" =~ /^$connectivity$/ AND "page" =~ /^$page$/ AND "summaryType" = 'pageSummary' AND "origin" = 'pagexray' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)

panels.title: Total Transfer Size

panels.description: The total size for all assets served for this page. This includes the uncompressed size for compressed text/css/html/js/font content.

targets.query: SELECT last("value") FROM "autogen"."contentSize" WHERE "group" =~ /^$group$/ AND "browser" =~ /^$browser$/ AND "connectivity" =~ /^$connectivity$/ AND "page" =~ /^$page$/ AND "summaryType" = 'pageSummary' AND "origin" = 'pagexray' AND "category" =~ /^$category$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)

panels.title: Total Content Size

panels.description: The performance score (0-100) calculated by the [Coach](https://www.sitespeed.io/documentation/coach/) using performance best practices.

targets.query: SELECT last("value") FROM "autogen"."score" WHERE "group" =~ /^$group$/ AND "browser" =~ /^$browser$/ AND "connectivity" =~ /^$connectivity$/ AND "page" =~ /^$page$/ AND "summaryType" = 'pageSummary' AND "advice" = 'performance' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)

panels.description: The time the browser takes to parse the document and execute deferred and parser-inserted scripts including the network time from the users location to your server.  It is collected using the Navigation Timing API by taking the domContentLoadedEventStart minus navigationStart.

targets.query: SELECT median("value") FROM "autogen"."domContentLoadedTime" WHERE "group" =~ /^$group$/ AND "page" =~ /^$page$/ AND "browser" =~ /^$browser$/ AND "connectivity" =~ /^$connectivity$/ AND "category" =~ /^$category$/ AND $timeFilter AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1h) fill(null)
